    "content": "<html><head></head><body><p class=\"sqsrte-large preFade fadeIn\">This seminar brings together scholars examining the development, credibility and social imaginaries of medical AI and health technologies. Join us on <strong>April 23 at the University of Helsinki’s Main Building (F3010, Fabianinkatu 33)</strong> <strong>from 14:00 to 17:00 </strong>for an afternoon of presentations and discussion.</p>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\"><strong>Chair: </strong>Matti Ylönen (University of Helsinki)</p>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\"><strong>Discussant: </strong>Kaire Holts (Tallinn University of Technology)</p>\n<h2 class=\"preFade fadeIn\"><strong>Programme </strong></h2>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\"><strong>14:00 Matti Ylönen (University of Helsinki) </strong></p>\n<p class=\"preFade fadeIn\"><em>Opening words</em></p>\n</body></html>",
